            </page_title>
            <p align="center"><stack item="arcanearchives:raw_quartz" scale="3.0"/></p>
            <horizontal_rule/>
            <p>
                Raw Quartz Clusters are a light source. They can be collected with a pick bearing the Silk Touch enchantment; otherwise breaking a Raw Quartz Cluster will return a piece of <link ref="RawQuartz">Raw Radiant Quartz</link>.
            </p>
            <p>
                <stack item="arcanearchives:radiant_resonator" /> Raw Quartz Clusters are created over time on top of a <link ref="RadiantResonator">Radiant Resonator</link>.
            </p>
