            </page_title>
            <p align="center"><stack item="arcanearchives:quartz_sliver" scale="3.0"/></p>
            <horizontal_rule/>
            <p>
                Slivers of Light are a light source, and an alternative to torches.
            </p>
            <p>
                <stack item="minecraft:stone"/> Slivers of Light can be crafted by bashing a piece of <link ref="RawQuartz">Raw Radiant Quartz</link> against another block. Each bash has a 40% chance of creating a single sliver, and a 20% chance of creating a handful of slivers but destroying the piece of Raw Radiant Quartz.
            </p>
            <horizontal_rule/>
        </section>
