            <p>
                <stack item="arcanearchives:item_scepterrevelation"/> Using a <link ref="ScepterRevelation">Scepter of Revelation</link> on a Monitoring Crystal will return what direction the Monitoring Crystal is pointing towards.
            </p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <p>
                <stack item="arcanearchives:gemcutters_table" /> Monitoring Crystals can be crafted on a <link ref="GemCuttersTable">Gem Cutter's Table</link>.
