            <horizontal_rule/>
            <p>
                A Radiant Trove is a storage container that can contain up to 64 stacks of a single type of item.
            </p>
            <p>
                <stack item="arcanearchives:item_component_materialinterface"/> By using a <link ref="MaterialInterface">Material Interface</link> while sneaking, the maximum capacity can be increased by 64 stacks. Up to 9 such upgrades can be applied total.
            </p>
            <p>
                <stack item="arcanearchives:item_scepterrevelation"/> Using a <link ref="ScepterRevelation">Scepter of Revelation</link> on a Radiant Trove will return what type of item is stored, its current and maximum capacity, and how many upgrades have been installed.
            </p>
        </section>
        <section>
