                <stack item="arcanearchives:item_sceptermanipulation"/> Using a <link ref="ScepterManipulation">Scepter of Manipulation</link> on a Radiant Trove will remove one installed upgrade, so long as the storage that upgrade provided is currently unused.
            </p>
            <horizontal_rule/>
            <p>
                <stack item="arcanearchives:gemcutters_table" /> Radiant Troves can be crafted on a <link ref="GemCuttersTable">Gem Cutter's Table</link>.
            </p>
