            <page_title>
                <title>Radiant Amphora</title>
            </page_title>
            <p align="center"><stack item="arcanearchives:item_radiantamphora" scale="3.0"/></p>
            <horizontal_rule/>
            <p>
                <stack item="arcanearchives:radiant_tank"/>A Radiant Amphora acts as a long distance connection to a specific <link ref="RadiantTank">Radiant Tank</link>. You can bind a Radiant Amphora to a Radiant Tank by using the amphora on the desired tank while sneaking. The amphora will become colorized to signify that a connection was made.
            </p>
            <p>
                <image src="arcanearchives:items/item_radiantamphora" tw="16" th="16"/> While in <span bold="true">Fill</span> mode, picking up fluid directly places it into the linked Radiant Tank.
            </p>
            <p>
                <image src="arcanearchives:items/item_radiantamphora_tilted" tw="16" th="16"/> When in <span bold="true">Empty</span> mode, fluid is removed from the linked Radiant Tank and placed at the target point.
            </p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <p>
                You can switch the Radiant Amphora's current mode by left clicking the air.
            </p>
            <horizontal_rule/>
            <p>
                <stack item="arcanearchives:gemcutters_table" /> Radiant Amphorae can be crafted on a <link ref="GemCuttersTable">Gem Cutter's Table</link>.
