            </page_title>
            <p align="center"><stack item="arcanearchives:item_rawquartz" scale="3.0"/></p>
            <horizontal_rule/>
            <p>
                Raw Radiant Quartz is an unrefined magical crystal that makes up the basis of all of Arcane Archives. It is primarily a crafting component.
            </p>
            <p>
                <stack item="minecraft:chest" /> Raw Radiant Quartz can be used to convert a chest to a <link ref="RadiantChest">Radiant Chest</link>.
            </p>
            <p>
                <stack item="minecraft:crafting_table" /> Raw Radiant Quartz can be used to convert a crafting table into a <link ref="RadiantCraftingTable">Radiant Crafting Table</link>.
            </p>
            <p>
                <stack item="arcanearchives:quartz_sliver" /> Raw Radiant Quartz can be used to create <link ref="DecorativeBlocks:SliverOfLight">Slivers of Light</link> by bashing a piece against another block.
            </p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <p>
                <stack item="arcanearchives:radiant_resonator" /> Raw Radiant Quartz is created over time on top of a <link ref="RadiantResonator">Radiant Resonator</link> in the form of a <link ref="DecorativeBlocks:RawQuartzCluster">Raw Quartz Cluster</link>.
            </p>
            <horizontal_rule/>
            <p italics="true">
