            <page_title>
                <title>Mountaintear</title>
            </page_title>
            <p align="center"><stack item="arcanearchives:item_mountaintear" scale="3.0"/></p>
            <horizontal_rule/>
            <p>
                <stack item="astralsorcery:blockwell"/> When placed in a Lightwell with access to the sky, a Mountaintear generates lava at a slow rate. While it's possible for a Mountaintear to shatter, the chances of shattering are <span italics="true">astronomically</span> unlikely. For all intents and purposes, a Mountaintear lasts indefinitely unless its Lightwell is broken.
            </p>
            <p>
                Once placed in a Lightwell, a Mountaintear cannot be retrieved.
            </p>
        </section>
